cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >-
  This Python package only repackages the State of the Union and Annual
  Message corpus curated by the UC Santa Barbara American Presidency
  Project. If you use this data in academic research, please cite the
  UCSB American Presidency Project as the primary source. A reference
  to this packaging is appreciated but secondary.
title: "sotu: U.S. Presidential Annual Messages and State of the Union Addresses (Python package)"
abstract: >-
  A Python package providing programmatic, offline access to the full
  corpus of U.S. Presidential Annual Messages (1790-1946) and State of
  the Union Addresses (1947-present). The text content is sourced
  verbatim from the UC Santa Barbara American Presidency Project; this
  package adds a pandas-DataFrame loader, NLTK-style file-id accessors,
  SHA-256 verification manifests, and an is_sotu flag distinguishing
  canonical SOTUs from related UCSB documents.
authors:
